  - `home_page.dart` updated to dispatch this event instead of directly requesti
ng nationwide ✓\n\n9. **Code quality issues**:\n   - In `matching_bloc.dart` `_o
nEmptyStateFallbackRequested`, if current state is `MatchingMatchCreated`, it de
faults to \'nearby\'. This is a minor edge case.\n   - The fallback logic `curre
ntMode == \'city\' ? \'nearby\' : \'nationwide\'` means if currentMode is someho
w \'nationwide\', it falls back to \'nationwide\' again. But the button is hidde
n in that mode.\n\n10. **API contract**: The `matching.controller.ts` returns `c
ode: 0` with proper structure. Good.\n\n11. **Accessibility**:\n    - `SwActionB
utton` uses `Semantics` with `identifier`, `label`, `button`, and `onTapDown` ✓\
