yRecommendationView` uses `Semantics` with `identifier` and `label` ✓\n    - `Ma
tchListItem` uses `Semantics` with `identifier`, `label`, `button`, and `onTapDo
wn` ✓\n    - `SwModeSelector` uses `Semantics` with `identifier` and `selected` 
