yaml\n- assertVisible:\n    text: "配对成功!"\n```\n\nBut you cannot combine sho
rthand with additional properties. So:\n```yaml\n- assertVisible: "配对成功!"\n 
optional: true\n```\n\nThis is indeed malformed YAML for Maestro. The `optional:
