rentState.mode,\n    ));\n  } else {\n    emit(MatchingMatchCreated(event.matchS
ummary));\n  }\n}\n```\n\nAnd in `_onMatchModalDismissed`:\n```dart\nvoid _onMat
chModalDismissed(\n  MatchModalDismissed event,\n  Emitter<MatchingState> emit,\
