\n  } else {\n    emit(MatchingMatchCreated(event.matchSummary));\n  }\n  ```\n 
`MatchingMatchCreated` 的默认值 `previousMode = \'nearby\'`。用户关闭弹窗后，`_o
nMatchModalDismissed` 会发射 `MatchingLoadEmpty(mode: \'nearby\')`，导致用户从「
